{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-18",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_18_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 18 - The Fall-Guy",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 9,
  "page_start_sec": 1226.7,
  "page_end_sec": 1470.1,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.691,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1226.7,
      "end": 1226.88,
      "text": "\"'Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1227.14,
      "end": 1228.92,
      "text": "they can only hang the punk once."
    },
    {
      "start": 1230.0,
      "end": 1231.11,
      "text": "Why try him for Jacoby's",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1231.38,
      "end": 1233.46,
      "text": "murder after he's been convicted of Thursby's?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1234.18,
      "end": 1235.06,
      "text": "They just close the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1235.18,
      "end": 1237.84,
      "text": "record by writing it up against him and let it go at that."
    },
    {
      "start": 1238.06,
      "end": 1238.16,
      "text": "If,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.0,
      "end": 1239.32,
      "text": "as is",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.46,
      "end": 1239.94,
      "text": "likely enough,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1240.22,
      "end": 1241.82,
      "text": "he used the same gun on both of them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1241.9,
      "end": 1243.34,
      "text": "the bullets will match up."
    },
    {
      "start": 1243.936,
      "end": 1244.64,
      "text": "Everybody will"
    },
    {
      "start": 1244.64,
      "end": 1245.728,
      "text": "be satisfied.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1246.92,
      "end": 1247.28,
      "text": "\"'Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1247.28,
      "end": 1247.76,
      "text": "but—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1248.672,
      "end": 1250.78,
      "text": "Gutman began and stopped to look at the boy.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1252.0,
      "end": 1253.4,
      "text": "The boy advanced from the doorway,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1253.72,
      "end": 1254.82,
      "text": "walking stiff-legged,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1254.96,
      "end": 1256.04,
      "text": "with his legs apart,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.3,
      "end": 1256.78,
      "text": "until he"
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.78,
      "end": 1258.34,
      "text": "was between Gutman and Cairo,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1258.52,
      "end": 1260.32,
      "text": "almost in the center of the floor."
    },
    {
      "start": 1261.72,
      "end": 1262.5,
      "text": "He halted there,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1262.68,
      "end": 1263.06,
      "text": "leaning"
    },
    {
      "start": 1263.2,
      "end": 1264.58,
      "text": "forward slightly from the waist,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1264.82,
      "end": 1266.76,
      "text": "his shoulders raised toward the front."
    },
    {
      "start": 1267.68,
      "end": 1268.7,
      "text": "The pistol in his hand",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1268.9,
      "end": 1270.0,
      "text": "still hung at his side,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1270.12,
      "end": 1272.42,
      "text": "but his knuckles were white over its grip."
    },
    {
      "start": 1273.72,
      "end": 1274.94,
      "text": "His other hand was a small,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1275.12,
      "end": 1277.04,
      "text": "hard fist down at his other side."
    },
    {
      "start": 1277.58,
      "end": 1281.36,
      "text": "The indelible youngness of his face gave an indescribably"
    },
    {
      "start": 1281.44,
      "end": 1284.24,
      "text": "vicious and inhuman turn to the white-hot hatred"
    },
    {
      "start": 1284.24,
      "end": 1286.9,
      "text": "and the cold white malevolence on his face."
    },
    {
      "start": 1287.56,
      "end": 1290.7,
      "text": "He said to Spade in a voice cramped by passion,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.35,
      "end": 1291.8,
      "text": "\"'You,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1292.52,
      "end": 1294.5,
      "text": "get up on your feet and go for your heater.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1295.44,
      "end": 1297.28,
      "text": "Spade smiled at the boy.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1297.56,
      "end": 1299.28,
      "text": "His smile was not broad,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1299.54,
      "end": 1301.54,
      "text": "but the amusement in it seemed genuine"
    },
    {
      "start": 1301.74,
      "end": 1302.68,
      "text": "and unalloyed."
    },
    {
      "start": 1303.41,
      "end": 1304.48,
      "text": "The boy said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1305.08,
      "end": 1305.28,
      "text": "\"'You!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1305.5,
      "end": 1307.94,
      "text": "Get up and shoot it out if you've got the guts."
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.64,
      "end": 1309.82,
      "text": "I've taken all the writing from",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1309.82,
      "end": 1310.75,
      "text": "you I'm going to take.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1312.3,
      "end": 1314.42,
      "text": "The amusement in Spade's smile deepened.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1315.2,
      "end": 1316.0,
      "text": "He looked at Gutman.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1317.184,
      "end": 1318.42,
      "text": "\"'Young Wild West,'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1319.08,
      "end": 1321.16,
      "text": "he said in a voice that matched his smile."
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.7,
      "end": 1324.62,
      "text": "Maybe you'd better remind him that shooting",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1324.62,
      "end": 1326.5,
      "text": "me before you get your hands on the Falcon"
    },
    {
      "start": 1326.66,
      "end": 1328.03,
      "text": "would be bad for business.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1329.696,
      "end": 1331.94,
      "text": "Gutman's attempt to smile was not successful,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1332.14,
      "end": 1334.8,
      "text": "but he kept the resultant grimace on his mottled"
    },
    {
      "start": 1334.9,
      "end": 1335.04,
      "text": "face."
    },
    {
      "start": 1336.06,
      "end": 1338.16,
      "text": "He licked his dry lips with a dry tongue.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1339.4,
      "end": 1341.56,
      "text": "His voice was too hoarse and gritty for the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1341.56,
      "end": 1343.98,
      "text": "paternally admonishing tone it tried to achieve."
    },
    {
      "start": 1345.76,
      "end": 1346.28,
      "text": "\"'Now come,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1346.46,
      "end": 1347.74,
      "text": "Wilmer,' he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 1348.1,
      "end": 1349.36,
      "text": "\"'We can't have any of that.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1349.38,
      "end": 1349.52,
      "text": "that."
    },
    {
      "start": 1349.92,
      "end": 1353.56,
      "text": "You shouldn't let yourself attach so much importance to these things."
    },
    {
      "start": 1353.96,
      "end": 1354.06,
      "text": "You—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1355.38,
      "end": 1355.88,
      "text": "The boy,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1356.04,
      "end": 1357.76,
      "text": "not taking his eyes from Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1357.9,
      "end": 1360.44,
      "text": "spoke in a choked voice out the side of his mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 1361.536,
      "end": 1362.38,
      "text": "\"'Make him lay off me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1362.46,
      "end": 1362.7,
      "text": "then."
    },
    {
      "start": 1363.03,
      "end": 1364.92,
      "text": "I'm going to plug him if he keeps it up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.0,
      "end": 1365.62,
      "text": "and there won't"
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.62,
      "end": 1367.616,
      "text": "be anything that will stop me from doing it.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.44,
      "end": 1369.08,
      "text": "\"'Now,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1369.08,
      "end": 1370.9,
      "text": "Wilmer,' Gutman said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1371.1,
      "end": 1372.12,
      "text": "and turned to Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 1373.28,
      "end": 1375.1,
      "text": "His face and voice were under control.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1376.64,
      "end": 1377.36,
      "text": "\"'Your plan is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1377.46,
      "end": 1377.64,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1377.78,
      "end": 1379.2,
      "text": "as I said in the first place,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1379.34,
      "end": 1380.46,
      "text": "not at all practical."
    },
    {
      "start": 1380.94,
      "end": 1383.104,
      "text": "Let's not say anything more about it.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1384.448,
      "end": 1386.26,
      "text": "Spade looked from one of them to the other.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1387.1,
      "end": 1388.16,
      "text": "He had stopped smiling.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1388.76,
      "end": 1390.9,
      "text": "His face held no expression at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 1392.28,
      "end": 1394.52,
      "text": "\"'I say what I please,' he told them.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1395.44,
      "end": 1397.76,
      "text": "\"'You certainly do,' Gutman said quickly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1398.42,
      "end": 1400.98,
      "text": "\"'and that's one of the things I've always admired in you."
    },
    {
      "start": 1401.84,
      "end": 1402.84,
      "text": "But this matter is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1403.06,
      "end": 1403.64,
      "text": "as I say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1403.78,
      "end": 1404.94,
      "text": "not at all practical,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1405.32,
      "end": 1408.78,
      "text": "so there's not the least bit of use of our discussing it any further,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1409.16,
      "end": 1410.7,
      "text": "as you can see for yourself.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1411.2,
      "end": 1414.36,
      "text": "\"'I can't see it for myself,' Spade argued,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1414.9,
      "end": 1416.48,
      "text": "\"'and you haven't made me see it.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1416.98,
      "end": 1418.44,
      "text": "He frowned at Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 1419.84,
      "end": 1420.7,
      "text": "\"'Let's get this straight.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1421.42,
      "end": 1423.12,
      "text": "Am I wasting time talking to you?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1423.5,
      "end": 1425.14,
      "text": "I thought this was your show."
    },
    {
      "start": 1426.336,
      "end": 1427.94,
      "text": "Should I do my talking to the punk?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1428.36,
      "end": 1429.8,
      "text": "I know how to do that.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1430.64,
      "end": 1430.96,
      "text": "\"'No,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1430.96,
      "end": 1432.28,
      "text": "sir,' Gutman replied."
    },
    {
      "start": 1433.0,
      "end": 1434.62,
      "text": "\"'You're quite right in dealing with me.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1435.904,
      "end": 1436.38,
      "text": "Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1437.12,
      "end": 1437.5,
      "text": "\"'All right.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1438.24,
      "end": 1439.52,
      "text": "Now I've got another suggestion.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1440.48,
      "end": 1440.92,
      "text": "It's not as",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1440.92,
      "end": 1441.82,
      "text": "good as the first one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1441.94,
      "end": 1443.18,
      "text": "but it's better than nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1443.96,
      "end": 1444.608,
      "text": "Want to hear it?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1445.376,
      "end": 1446.56,
      "text": "\"'Most assuredly.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1447.584,
      "end": 1448.23,
      "text": "\"'Give them Cairo.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1450.016,
      "end": 1453.04,
      "text": "Cairo hastily picked his pistol up from the table beside him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1453.74,
      "end": 1454.18,
      "text": "He held it",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1454.22,
      "end": 1455.84,
      "text": "tight in his lap with both hands."
    },
    {
      "start": 1456.76,
      "end": 1458.3,
      "text": "Its muzzle pointed at the floor a",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1458.3,
      "end": 1459.64,
      "text": "little to one side of the sofa."
    },
    {
      "start": 1460.78,
      "end": 1462.54,
      "text": "His face had become yellowish again.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1462.86,
      "end": 1463.008,
      "text": "His"
    },
    {
      "start": 1463.48,
      "end": 1465.94,
      "text": "black eyes darted their gaze from face to face."
    },
    {
      "start": 1466.88,
      "end": 1469.26,
      "text": "The opaqueness of his eyes made them seem flat,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1469.62,
      "end": 1470.1,
      "text": "two-dimensional."
    }
  ]
}